premise_source_doc_sentence: Seven seasons have completed airing in the United States , with 12 episodes in the first season , 16 episodes in the second and third seasons , and 18 episodes in the fourth season .
The show 's fifth season , comprising 18 episodes , began airing June 23 , 2011 , and entered a mid-season break after twelve episodes on September 8 , 2011 .
NBC had originally announced that Scrubs would end after its seventh season , containing a reduced 18 episodes .
